A ring bearing the Adventurers' Guild crest.

The Adventuring ring item is a loot item.

Requirement

  • Have character level [20].

Attributes

Global +0.5% Chance to find 1 Adventurers' guild token
Global +2% Work efficiency
Requires [1] unique Adventuring tool set equipped.
Global +2% Chest finding
Requires [2] unique Adventuring tool set equipped.
Global +3% Fine material finding
Requires [3] unique Adventuring tool set equipped.
Global +2% Double rewards
Requires [4] unique Adventuring tool set equipped.
Global -1 Steps required
Requires [5] unique Adventuring tool set equipped.

Uses

Mysterious Merchant
